<p class="govuk-body-l govuk-!-margin-top-6">
  You have just experienced a tool built by a UK council, for UK councils, that transforms
  how public services communicate with residents. In 25 minutes, you have seen what Swindon
  Borough Council built to make documents accessible to everyone -- and it is open source
  for any organisation to use.
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">What you've learned</h2>

<div class="ndx-takeaway-grid">
  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Document Translation
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Translate documents into 75 languages in minutes while preserving formatting.
      Amazon Translate handles the heavy lifting at a fraction of traditional costs.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: 99.96% cost reduction -- from &pound;160 to &pound;0.07 per document
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Easy Read with AI
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Create Easy Read documents with AI-simplified text and generated images.
      Co-created with Experts by Experience to ensure genuine accessibility.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: ~1p per page vs &pound;120 per page with traditional production
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Open Source
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      This is an AWS Sample, freely available on GitHub. Any council can deploy it
      into their own AWS account with no licensing fees.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: No vendor lock-in, community-driven improvements
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Built by Local Government
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Pioneered by Swindon Borough Council and now adopted by Edinburgh, Newport,
      Southampton, West Berkshire, and others. Real public sector innovation.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Proven in production by UK councils
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

